# Build context is the repo root (docker build -f apps/<app>/Dockerfile .).
# Keep the context lean and never ship host artifacts or secrets into the image.

# Installed deps + build output — rebuilt fresh inside the image
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# VCS + local tooling
.git
.github
worktrees

# Secrets / local env — MUST NOT enter the build context
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Docs, audit, and the engineering-OS trail — not needed at build/runtime
docs
.engineering-os
**/*.md
README.md

# Test/coverage/editor noise
**/coverage
**/.vitest
**/playwright-report
**/test-results
**/.DS_Store
**/*.log
